Spatial Eigenvectors - adespatial package:



############ load adespaial   #####################

library(adespatial)
library(adegraphics)

###########          ########################

## spatial site data
sp.dat<-readRDS('./rdm_model_output/spDataSiteRep.RDS')

weekly.hist<-readRDS('./rdm_model_output/weeklyCaptHist.rmd')

sites<-weekly.hist %>% 
  group_by(yr_cell_site) %>% 
  summarize(yr_cell_site = yr_cell_site[1]) %>% 
  pull(yr_cell_site)

site.dat<-as_tibble(sp.dat$siteLocations) %>% 
  mutate(yr_cell_site = sites) %>% 
  select(yr_cell_site, utme, utmn)

############ create neighbors  #####################

adjacent.sites <- chooseCN(sp.dat$siteLocations, type = 1, plot.nb = F)
#str(adjacent.sites)

s.Spatial(sp.dat$siteLocations, 
          nb = adjacent.sites, 
          plabel.cex = 0, 
          ppoints.fill = "#F98400",
          pnb.edge.col = "#C93312", 
          pbackground.col = "#899DA4"

          )


############ adjust neighbors by year and distance   #####################

adjacent.sites<-nb.by.yr.maxd(nb = adjacent.sites,
              locs.site = coordinates(sp.dat$siteLocations),
              yr.v.site = sp.dat$siteYear,
              max.dist = 7) 

s.Spatial(sp.dat$siteLocations, 
          nb = adjacent.sites, 
          plabel.cex = 0, 
          ppoints.fill = "#F98400",
          pnb.edge.col = "#C93312", 
          pbackground.col = "#899DA4"

          )


############ convert to weights   #####################


## list of distance
adj.dists <- nbdists(adjacent.sites, sp.dat$siteLocations)

## list of weieg
adj.weights <- lapply(adj.dists, function(x) 1 - x/max(dist(sp.dat$siteLocations)))


weights.list <- nb2listw(adjacent.sites, style = 'W', glist = adj.weights, zero.policy = TRUE)
# str(weights.list)
mono.index <- which(sp.dat$siteYear == '2018')

wt.mat<-round(listw2mat(weights.list)[mono.index, mono.index], digits = 3)

rownames(wt.mat)<-substring(sites[mono.index],6,20)
colnames(wt.mat)<-rownames(wt.mat)
  
wt.mat[c(1:8),c(1:8)]

############ create spatial eigenvectors   #####################

## mems 
eigen.list<-mem(weights.list)
# str(eigen.vals.l)
eigen.vals <- attr(eigen.list, 'values')
eigen.mat<-as.matrix(eigen.list)
#eigen.mat<-eigen.mat[, abs(eigen.vals) > .015 ]
eigen.mat <- eigen.mat[,eigen.vals > 0]
n.eigen<-ncol(eigen.mat)

############ plot eigenvectors all sites   #####################

mem.in <- eigen.mat[,c(1,5,10,15,20,30,40,45,50)] %>% 
  as_tibble() %>% 
  mutate(site = sites,
         utme = sp.dat$siteLocations[,'utme'],
         utmn = sp.dat$siteLocations[,'utmn'],) %>%
  #slice(mono.index) %>% 
  pivot_longer(!c(site,utme,utmn), names_to = 'mem', values_to = 'mem_val') %>% 
  mutate(sign = ifelse(mem_val > 0, 1, -1)) %>% 
  mutate(mem_val = abs(mem_val)) %>% 
  mutate(mem = factor(mem, levels = colnames(eigen.mat[,c(1,5,10,15,20,30,40,45,50)])))
  

my_colors <- c( "#00A08A", "#F98400")
ggplot(mem.in)+
  geom_point(aes(x=utme, y=utmn, size = mem_val, color = factor(sign)))+
  scale_color_manual(values = my_colors) +
  facet_wrap(~ factor(mem))


############ plot eigenvectors mono creek sites  #####################

mem.in <- eigen.mat[,c(1,5,10,15,20,30,40,45,50)] %>% 
  as_tibble() %>% 
  mutate(site = sites,
         utme = sp.dat$siteLocations[,'utme'],
         utmn = sp.dat$siteLocations[,'utmn'],) %>%
  slice(mono.index) %>% 
  pivot_longer(!c(site,utme,utmn), names_to = 'mem', values_to = 'mem_val') %>% 
  mutate(sign = ifelse(mem_val > 0, 1, -1)) %>% 
  mutate(mem_val = abs(mem_val)) %>% 
  mutate(mem = factor(mem, levels = colnames(eigen.mat[,c(1,5,10,15,20,30,40,45,50)])))
  


my_colors <- c( "#00A08A", "#F98400")
ggplot(mem.in)+
  geom_point(aes(x=utme, y=utmn, size = mem_val, color = factor(sign)))+
  scale_color_manual(values = my_colors) +
  facet_wrap(~ factor(mem))
